                  <span class="c00">If you love spelling and hyphenation, you should star this issue in Chrome(ium):<p><a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;code.google.com&#x2F;p&#x2F;chromium&#x2F;issues&#x2F;detail?id=20667" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;code.google.com&#x2F;p&#x2F;chromium&#x2F;issues&#x2F;detail?id=20667</a><p>There are a lots of spelling and hyphenation libraries e.g. for Finnish language, but it is not possible to get them to working in Chrome cause there is no extension capability for it. It&#x27;s really shame, since these odd languages probably never get support by Chrome team itself.<span>
